Deploying a snapshot:

 % mvn clean
 % mvn deploy -Prelease

Preparing a release (dry run):

 % mvn clean
 % mvn release:prepare -DdryRun=true -DautoVersionSubmodules=true -Prelease
 <enter your gpg passphrase>

Preparing a release:

 % mvn clean
 % mvn release:prepare -DautoVersionSubmodules=true -Prelease
 <enter your gpg passphrase>

Performing a release:

 % mvn release:perform -Prelease
 <enter your gpg passphrase>
